{"tid":914682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瞓咗冇睇，屯門建生邨750萬賣咗未？","createTime":"2018-11-24T13:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T13:17:11.000Z","uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a1930ce09e64767542b58ea2c69522c0a2f9de8d","tid":914682,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"白居二計劃即將重推之際，屯門公屋建生邨一個高層500多呎單位，自由市場價叫價800萬，業主雖現已鬆口減至750萬，但呎價達13,787元。750萬在建生邨買間公屋，你又覺得買得過？<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產的官網介紹，放售的公屋單位為屯門建生邨泰生樓的高層3房單位，實用面積544呎，在自由市場叫價750萬，即呎價13,787元，超越不少藍籌屋邨。根據中原地產資料，近期藍田麗港城實用呎價$13,191，美孚新邨呎價$13,329。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，業主早於1989年已買入該單位，近期有意求售，最初曾一度叫價800萬，但業主見放盤一個月仍乏人問津，已減價求售，但仍高叫750萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/211017_c8b86356dc4def28ec1e8da33aeb738b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F211017_c8b86356dc4def28ec1e8da33aeb738b.png&h=b109db2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/211019_27f684d9d643598055836919b7c0c275.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F211019_27f684d9d643598055836919b7c0c275.png&h=f24d8ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/211021_e2f8a0857ad525d5ae9f30186a97fb33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F211021_e2f8a0857ad525d5ae9f30186a97fb33.png&h=5cc04560&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/211023_ec8a31512aaab5c9de247c007cc8fb5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F211023_ec8a31512aaab5c9de247c007cc8fb5e.png&h=39033a89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d554ace532fd108e7eb9810b477afa2a115034e","tid":914682,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]